<section id="gnome">
<title>Gnome Compliance</title>
<para>Fvwm attempts to be <acronym>GNOME</acronym> (version 1) compliant.
Check <ulink url='http://www.gnome.org'>http://www.gnome.org</ulink>
for what that may mean. To disable <acronym>GNOME</acronym> hints for some
or all windows, the
<fvwmref cmd="Style" opt="GNOMEIgnoreHints"/>
style can be used.</para>
</section>

